overview:
Sebastian Gutsfeld is one of the two main developers of TheDeadline.

Having worked on Java and Scala based web applications and different audio synthesis languages he currently enjoys coding, exploring and extending the new Lisp dialect Clojure in combination with Javascript and the cloud infrastructure of Google App Engine.

Before working on TheDeadline Sebastian was implementing e-commerce systems at freiheit.com technologies gmbh. During his course of studies he worked as a programmer for Infineon Technologies AG in Munich.
